---
title: Cheesy Sweet Corn Dip Serves 2 |with Garlic Flatbread Chips
description: Whether you're hosting game night or a dinner party, guests will scoop up every last bite of this cheesy sweet corn appetizer! Layers of bright corn, mozzarella cheese, chives and cream cheese come together to make an oh-so-sweet restaurant-worthy dip.
